<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$danco" href="/people/danco">Danco</a>，<strong title="http://blog.sina.com.cn/sheepme" class="zu-question-my-bio"><a href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/sheepme" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">blog.sina.com.cn/sheepm</span><span class="invisible">e</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a></strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="40">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lin-de-man" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lin-de-man" class="zg-link" title="林德曼">林德曼</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-qin-11-51" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-qin-11-51" class="zg-link" title="张钦">张钦</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$tianming9595" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/tianming9595" class="zg-link" title="天赋">天赋</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="147223" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">因为人们喜欢即时反馈。<br><br>不管结果是赔是赚，只要下注，马上就能知道结果。<br><br>游戏、人人、微博、撸管……都是利用了此弱点于是应运而生。<br><br>在这样的恶性循环下，耐心渐渐变成了难得的品质。人们不愿等待，不愿投入时间，疯狂追求快速致富、一周减肥、一个月外语速成……
